text: The Nanny is a 1965 British horror movie directed by Seth Holt and based on the novel of the same name by Merriam Modell. It stars Bette Davis, Wendy Craig, Jill Bennett, James Villiers, Harry Fowler, Maurice Denham and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1965 horror movies Category:British horror movies Category:Movies directed by Seth Holt Category:20th Century Fox movies
title: The Nanny (1965 movie)
